# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# .gitignore for the React Native New Architecture Research book
#
# This is a documentation repo (markdown chapters + audit workspace). It is
# not a build target. Patterns below cover OS / editor / audit-workspace
# noise. Keep this file conservative; if a future contributor wants to track
# something matched here, they can use `git add -f`.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

# -------- OS metadata --------
.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
._*
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes
ehthumbs.db
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# -------- Editor / IDE --------
.vscode/
.idea/
*.iml
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.fleet/
.zed/
.cursor/
.history/
*.code-workspace
nbproject/

# -------- Audit workspace --------
# The chapter audit lives under _verification/ (see docs/audit-workflow.md
# if added). It contains per-chapter claims, tests, reports, and HTTP debug
# dumps that should not be committed. Sub-paths called out explicitly so
# a contributor running the audit knows what's intentionally local.
_verification/

# Debug dumps from minimal-agent's MINIMAL_AGENT_NET_DBG=1 flag (per-cwd)
.net-dbg/

# -------- Node / Bun / package managers --------
node_modules/
.pnp/
.pnp.*
.yarn/cache
.yarn/install-state.gz
.npm/
.pnpm-store/
.bun/

# Lockfiles: leave UNCOMMITTED in this docs repo since there is no app to
# pin. If a future apps/ subdir wants its own lockfile, this can be relaxed
# per-subdirectory with a nested .gitignore.
bun.lock
bun.lockb
package-lock.json
yarn.lock
pnpm-lock.yaml

# -------- Build outputs --------
dist/
build/
out/
.next/
.nuxt/

# -------- Test / coverage / cache --------
coverage/
.nyc_output/
.cache/
.parcel-cache/
.turbo/
.vitest-cache/

# -------- Logs and tmp --------
*.log
logs/
tmp/
temp/
*.tmp

# -------- Env / secrets (defensive; no app here, but never commit these) --------
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# -------- Misc backups --------
*.bak
*.orig
*.rej

# -------- Python (in case any verification script uses it) --------
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
.venv/
venv/

# -------- Common scratch from automated agents --------
PROGRESS.md.bak
*.tmp.md
